<!-- SLIDE 3: THE PROBLEM -->
<div class="slide">
    <div class="header">
        <div class="header-content">
            <h1>Current State: Key Issues</h1>
            <p>Significant operational and financial risks identified</p>
        </div>
        <div class="header-logo">
            <div class="logo-text">
                <div class="logo-main">
                    <span class="logo-better">BETTER</span><span class="logo-gov">GOV</span>
                </div>
                <div class="logo-tagline">
                    <span class="logo-digitally">Digitally Driven, Socially </span><span class="logo-empowered">Empowered</span>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
        <h2>Critical Challenges Impacting Operations</h2>
        
        <div class="issue-box">
            <h4>üî¥ Financial Risk</h4>
            <p>Significant debt management issues, loss of income from delayed/inaccurate financial assessments, and overpayment risks particularly in high-cost Children's placements.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="issue-box">
            <h4>‚öôÔ∏è Process Complexity</h4>
            <p>Overly complex, manual processes across multiple systems (CM2000, Kefron, Oracle, bespoke "black box"). Heavy reliance on spreadsheets and manual checks creating bottlenecks.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="issue-box">
            <h4>üë• Unclear Accountability</h4>
            <p>Fragmented responsibilities across Adults, Children's, and Corporate Finance teams. Several hundred open resident queries with no clear ownership.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="issue-box">
            <h4>üìä Limited Visibility</h4>
            <p>Fragmented reporting, limited access to Mosaic reports, and no proactive dashboards. Reduces oversight and control of critical financial activity.</p>
        </div>

        <div style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fef3c7 0%, #fde68a 100%); padding: 15px; border-radius: 8px; margin-top: 16px; border-left: 4px solid #d97706;">
            <div style="font-size: 14px; color: #92400e; font-weight: bold; margin-bottom: 8px;">‚ö†Ô∏è Impact Without Action</div>
            <div style="font-size: 12px; color: #78350f; line-height: 1.5;">
                Continued financial risk exposure, resident dissatisfaction, supplier relationship damage, and potential regulatory/Ombudsman challenges. Current inefficiencies consume substantial staff time better deployed elsewhere.
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
        <div><strong>Better Group Limited ¬© 2025.</strong> This document contains proprietary information and is provided on the express basis of confidence.</div>
        <div class="slide-number">3</div>
    </div>
</div>

<!-- SLIDE 4: THE SOLUTION -->
<div class="slide">
    <div class="header">
        <div class="header-content">
            <h1>Proposed Solution</h1>
            <p>Comprehensive modernization programme across 28 workstreams</p>
        </div>
        <div class="header-logo">
            <div class="logo-text">
                <div class="logo-main">
                    <span class="logo-better">BETTER</span><span class="logo-gov">GOV</span>
                </div>
                <div class="logo-tagline">
                    <span class="logo-digitally">Digitally Driven, Socially </span><span class="logo-empowered">Empowered</span>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
        <h2>Four Strategic Themes</h2>
        
        <div class="solution-grid">
            <div class="solution-item">
                <h4>üí∞ Streamline Payments & Suppliers</h4>
                <ul>
                    <li>Implement Mosaic Provider Portal to replace CM2000 homecare system</li>
                    <li>Automate client contributions</li>
                    <li>Retire "black box" application</li>
                    <li>Enable remittance emails from Mosaic</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            
            <div class="solution-item">
                <h4>üëî Clarify Roles & Operations</h4>
                <ul>
                    <li>Develop Target Operating Model</li>
                    <li>Automate Financial Assessment (FA) annual uplifts</li>
                    <li>Review end-to-end Financial Assessment process</li>
                    <li>Create dedicated Payments & Billing teams</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            
            <div class="solution-item">
                <h4>‚öôÔ∏è Optimize Mosaic Configuration</h4>
                <ul>
                    <li>Simplify purchasing elements</li>
                    <li>Rationalize payment cycle types</li>
                    <li>Review report permissions</li>
                    <li>Implement Power BI dashboards</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            
            <div class="solution-item">
                <h4>üåê Improve Resident Engagement</h4>
                <ul>
                    <li>Enhance digital Financial Assessment portal</li>
                    <li>Integrate with Mosaic APIs</li>
                    <li>Reduce manual data entry</li>
                    <li>Improve billing transparency</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div style="background: #f0f9ff; padding: 15px; border-radius: 6px; margin-top: 20px; border-left: 4px solid #0284c7;">
            <div style="font-size: 13px; color: #005a7d; font-weight: bold; margin-bottom: 8px;">üìã Comprehensive Scope</div>
            <div style="font-size: 11px; color: #475569; line-height: 1.5;">
                <strong>15 recommendations for Adults Finance</strong> and <strong>13 for Children's Finance</strong>, prioritized as High, Medium, or Low based on risk, impact, and effort. Full delivery estimated at <strong>~900 days specialist effort + 160 days SME input</strong> over approximately 12 months.
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
